  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Dietary intervention to prevent sarcopenia in elderly people. The objective of this study is
      to test whether meat structure plays an important role in protein digestion, to maximise the
      amino acid availability and to stimulate the muscle protein growth in elderly people.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
